name: iPhone 5 Vibe Case, or iPhone 4,4S Vibe case in any one of my art designs
description:
This listing is for a choice of any ONE of the Case designs in the picture for the iPhone 5 or 4/4s Vibe Case. 

**When checking out please include the name of the design you would like for the Vibe case.

My artwork is printed / imbedded into this wonderfully sleek Vibe iPhone tough case created by Case-Mate. The art also completely wraps around and covers the edges for a beautiful seamless look while still showing of the fabulous look of your device.

Vibe case details-- 
Two piece protection--a tough, polycarbonate hard shell and accompanying rigid bumper join together for a secure fit. A unique contoured profile offers an enhanced grip and allows the case to stand upright on its own. Along with a cushioned interior layer provides soft, impact-absorbing protection and is detailed with a nice textured pattern.
Exclusive Soundscoop design redirects speaker audio towards you, instead of down, for enhanced sound projection.

Please allow 3-5 business days before item is processed and shipped out. Each case is custom made to order. Shipping will take an additional 2-4 days via Priority Mail. USA only

Please contact me with any questions at all.
Thank you so much!! :):)
Ingrid
